步骤：
1. install mongodb on mac:
sudo port install mongodb
mkdir /opt/local/data
mkdir /opt/local/data/db
cd /opt/local/bin
sudo ./mongod --dbpath /opt/local/data/db/

2. install nodejs on mac:
brew install node
或
sudo port install nodejs

3. setup repo:
git clone git@github.com:zhengjianing/TWCourse.git
cd TWCourse
npm install
node app (或开启debug模式：1.启动debugger：node-inspector; 2.启动server：node --debug app )
visit localhost:3000


